sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron as Vercel Cron
    participant Scraper as Serverless Function
    participant Source as AAStocks / News Sites
    participant AI_CL as minimax-m2.5
    participant AI_DS as DeepSeek V3
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant App as Next.js UI
    participant Agent as AIA Agent

    rect rgb(219, 234, 254)
    Note over Cron,Agent: Daily Price Collection (7pm HKT)
    Cron->>Scraper: Trigger price scraper
    Scraper->>Source: Fetch fund prices HTML
    Source-->>Scraper: HTML response
    Scraper->>Scraper: Parse with Cheerio
    Scraper->>DB: Upsert mpf_prices
    Scraper->>Scraper: Check outliers > 2%
    end

    rect rgb(254, 226, 226)
    alt Fund moved > 2%
        Scraper->>AI_DS: Generate alert insight
        AI_DS-->>DB: Store mpf_insights
        DB-->>App: Push notification badge
    end
    end

    rect rgb(254, 243, 199)
    Note over Cron,Agent: News Collection (Every 6hrs)
    Cron->>Scraper: Trigger news scraper
    Scraper->>Source: Fetch news articles
    Source-->>Scraper: HTML response
    Scraper->>AI_CL: Classify news
    AI_CL-->>Scraper: sentiment + impact_tags + region
    Scraper->>DB: Insert mpf_news + mpf_fund_news
    end

    rect rgb(254, 226, 226)
    alt High impact news
        Scraper->>AI_DS: Generate full insight refresh
        AI_DS-->>DB: Store mpf_insights
        DB-->>App: Push notification badge
    end
    end

    rect rgb(209, 250, 229)
    Note over Cron,Agent: Weekly Insight Profile (Sunday)
    Cron->>Scraper: Trigger insight generation
    Scraper->>DB: Gather week prices + news
    Scraper->>AI_DS: Full portfolio analysis
    AI_DS-->>Scraper: AIA MPF Care Profile (EN + ZH)
    Scraper->>DB: Store mpf_insights
    end

    rect rgb(237, 233, 254)
    Note over App,Agent: Agent Usage
    Agent->>App: Open /mpf-care
    App->>DB: Query latest data
    DB-->>App: Funds + prices + news + insights
    App-->>Agent: Overview / Fund Explorer / News / Insights
    end
